title: Upper Level House - With All Utilities Included!
posting_body: ['Hi everyone,', 'I have a private upper level house that is available for rent starting mid to late August, 2022 in my home.', 'The home is located in West Bloomington near the W Bush Lake Park area in a nice quiet neighborhood and it’s in excellent condition.', '(4 Bedrooms + 2 Bathrooms).', 'The upper level of this house for rent includes a privet entry, private master bathroom, the whole living room space, 3 bedrooms, private kitchen.', 'The rent will be $1895 per month and the security deposits will be $3000 that INCLUDES ALL: (gas, water, electricity, trash, internet, lawn care, snowplowing).', 'The total area is about 1300 plus sq ft.', 'The lease term will be yearly with an option to extend.', 'I am looking for a long term renter after an initial trial period.', 'Also, full access to drive way parking, shared laundry room, garage storage (within reasonable) available for bikes etc.', 'Clear background check and proof of income will be required.', 'About me:', 'I am a professional in my 30’s and looking for an individual or couple’s who are also a working professional, I have no pets and like to keep a clean and organized home, and expect the potential renters to do the same.', 'Please contact me by replying if you are interested.', 'Tell me a bit about yourself and we can go from there.', 'Thanks']
